# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok say hey to marc clarke , ## , college student , big brother , dutiful son , giving boyfriend , charity giver , aspiring lawyer , `` jerry springer '' devotee .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (y / you)
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Marc"
                        :op2 "Clarke"))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (s2 / study-01
                        :location (c / college)))
            :op3 (p3 / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG2 (b / brother))
                  :mod (b2 / big))
            :op4 (p4 / person
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG2 (b3 / boyfriend)))
            :op5 (p5 / person
                  :ARG0-of (g / give-01
                        :ARG1 (c2 / charity)))
            :op6 (p6 / person
                  :ARG0-of (a2 / aspire-01
                        :ARG1 (l / lawyer)))
            :op7 (p7 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Jerry"
                        :op2 "Springer")
                  :ARG1-of (d / devote-01)))
      :ARG2 y
      :mod (h3 / hey))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the top u.s. and nato commander in afghanistan is visiting the site of an airstrike where villagers reportedly died when american jets bombed two fuel tankers hijacked by the taliban .
# ::alignments
(v / visit-01
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))
                        :ARG2 (c2 / commander
                              :mod (t / top))))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (m / military
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "NATO"))
                        :ARG2 (c3 / commander
                              :mod (t2 / top))))
            :location (c4 / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Afghanistan")))
      :ARG1 (s / site
            :location-of (d / die-01
                  :ARG1 (v2 / villager)
                  :ARG1-of (r / report-01)
                  :ARG1-of (c5 / cause-01
                        :ARG0 (b / bomb-01
                              :ARG0 (j / jet
                                    :mod (c6 / country
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "America")))
                              :ARG1 (t3 / tanker
                                    :quant 2
                                    :mod (f / fuel)
                                    :ARG1-of (h3 / hijack-01
                                          :ARG0 (c7 / criminal-organization
                                                :name (n5 / name
                                                      :op1 "Taliban")))))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok for wall street , investing anywhere simply means getting a good return on funds spent .
# ::alignments
(m / mean-01
      :ARG1 (ii / invest-01
            :ARG2 (a / anywhere))
      :ARG2 (g / get-01
            :ARG0 (m2 / market-sector
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Wall"
                        :op2 "Street"))
            :ARG1 (r / return-05
                  :ARG1 (f / fund
                        :ARG3-of (s / spend-01))
                  :ARG1-of (g2 / good-02)))
      :ARG1-of (s2 / simple-02))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :weekday (m / monday)))
      :op2 (h / hold-back-07
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (c3 / crop
                  :poss p)
            :ARG2 (p2 / protest-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (p3 / price-01
                              :ARG1-of (l / low-04)
                              :mod (r / retail-01))
                        :op2 (t / tax-01
                              :ARG3 (e / export-01)
                              :ARG1-of (h2 / high-02))))
            :ARG1-of (m2 / move-02
                  :ARG0-of (a4 / affect-01
                        :ARG1 (c4 / crop
                              :mod (c5 / cocoa)
                              :mod (w / world))
                        :ARG1-of (p4 / possible-01)))))

                        :mod (s / secret)
                        :poss c)
                  :ARG1-of (r / report-01)))
      :ARG2 (p2 / person
            :ARG0-of (r2 / receive-01
                  :ARG1 (a3 / award-01
                        :ARG1 (h / health)
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
                        :ARG1-of (g / give-01
                              :ARG0 (a4 / and
                                    :op1 (g2 / group
                                          :mod (c2 / country
                                                :name (n4 / name
                                                      :op1 "U.S.")))
                                    :op2 (g3 / group
                                          :mod (c3 / country
                                                :name (n5 / name
                                                      :op1 "Canada")))))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))))

                        :quant 1

                  :ARG0 c

                        :op1 (n / now)
                        :duration (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 4
                              :unit (m2 / month)))))
      :ARG1 (b2 / back-01
            :ARG0 (c3 / citizen
                  :mod (c4 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Eu"))
                  :quant (m3 / majority))
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (c5 / currency
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / single-02))
                  :op2 (p2 / policy-01
                        :ARG2 (f / foreign)
                        :mod (c6 / common))
                  :op3 (s3 / step-01
                        :ARG2 (d / defend-01
                              :mod c6)))))

                              :mod (s5 / suicide))
                        :ARG0-of (w / wound-01
                              :mod c)
                        :ARG1-of w))
            :location (o / outside
                  :op1 (c2 / cafe
                        :ARG1-of (p2 / pack-01)))

                  :quant 1
                  :unit (d3 / day))))

                                                :op1 "Israel"))
                                    :ARG2 (m / minister
                                          :mod (p2 / prime)))))))
      :ARG1 (d / decide-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Security"
                        :op2 "Cabinet")
                  :poss c)
            :ARG1 (a / allow-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (e / export-01
                        :ARG0 (p3 / person
                              :ARG0-of (r2 / reside-01
                                    :ARG1 (s3 / strip
                                          :mod (c2 / city
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Gaza")))))
                        :ARG1 (r3 / range
                              :mod (g2 / good)
                              :ARG1-of (w / wide-02
                                    :ARG2-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG1 r3
                                          :ARG3 (m2 / more))))
                        :ARG2 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (c3 / country-region
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "West"
                                          :op2 "Bank"))
                              :op2 (o2 / overseas))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (w2 / wednesday))))
